21:46.653 --> 21:49.220
♪ YOU SAY THAT YOU WANT ME BACK ♪

21:49.351 --> 21:53.616
♪ TO THE WAY WE THAT USED TO BE

21:55.096 --> 22:01.102
♪ BUT YOU JUST NEVER WILL SEE

22:04.366 --> 22:10.024
♪ HOW CAN YOU EVER ASK THIS THING OF ME?

22:10.154 --> 22:12.940
♪ CAN YOU GIVE YOURSELF?

22:14.333 --> 22:17.336
♪ I KNOW YOU SAID IT

22:18.424 --> 22:21.252
♪ BUT YOU ONCE WERE MINE

